2012年7月18日在[[保加利亚|保加利亚]][[布尔加斯|布尔加斯]]的[[布尔加斯机场|布尔加斯机场]]附近发生了一起[[自杀攻击|自杀式炸弹袭击]]事件。<ref name="fakeUSID">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/20/world/europe/explosion-on-bulgaria-tour-bus-kills-at-least-five-israelis.html?pagewanted=all|title=Suicide Attacker With Fake U.S. ID Blamed in Bus Bomb|publisher=New York Times|author=Kulish, Nicholas|date=19 July 2012|accessdate=19 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120726020201/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/20/world/europe/explosion-on-bulgaria-tour-bus-kills-at-least-five-israelis.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nrg.co.il/online/1/ART2/387/813.html?hp=1&cat=666&loc=1|accessdate=19 July 2012|date=19 July 2012|publisher=Ynet!|title=משרד החוץ: מניין ההרוגים ירד לשבעה, בהם 6 ישראלים|language=he|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721235940/http://www.nrg.co.il/online/1/ART2/387/813.html?hp=1&cat=666&loc=1|archive-date=2012-07-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>被炸车辆装载了42名[[以色列|以色列]]人，且以年轻人为主，<ref name="Youth">{{cite web|url=http://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=141422|title=Blasted Israeli tourists in Bulgaria mostly youth|publisher=Novinite|date=18 July 2012|accessdate=18 July 2012|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203033138/https://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=141422|dead-url=no}}</ref>这些乘客来自[[特拉维夫|特拉维夫]]，乘坐[[Air_VIA|Air VIA]]的航班，抵达机场后正赶往旅馆。<ref name="NoviniteBlast">{{cite web|url=http://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=141416|title=Israeli tourists in Bulgaria attacked with grenades, Hezbollah TV says|publisher=Novinite|date=18 July 2012|accessdate=18 July 2012|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205082601/https://www.novinite.com/view_news.php?id=141416|dead-url=no}}</ref>这次爆炸造成包括自杀式袭击者和大巴司机在内的共7人死亡，至少32人受伤，引起国际关注。

爆炸两个小时后[[以色列|以色列]]总理[[内塔尼亚胡|内塔尼亚胡]]谴责[[伊朗|伊朗]]与黎巴嫩[[真主党|真主党]]。这一袭击与[[1994年犹太人文化中心爆炸事件|1994年犹太人文化中心爆炸事件]]是同一天，那次爆炸案就是被怀疑是[[伊朗|伊朗]]与[[真主党|真主党]]制造的。<ref name="PMORemarks">{{cite press_release | url=http://www.pmo.gov.il/PMOEng/Communication/Spokesman/2012/07/spokeBulg180712.htm | title=PM Netanyahu's Remarks Following the Terror Attack in Bulgaria | publisher=The Prime Minister's Office | date=18 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | archive-date=2019-09-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902085633/http://www.pmo.gov.il/PMOEng/Communication/Spokesman/2012/07/spokeBulg180712.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/138780/bulgarian-president-mossad-did-not-warn-attack-was-coming.html Bulgarian President: Mossad did not Warn Attack was Coming] {{Wayback|url=http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/138780/bulgarian-president-mossad-did-not-warn-attack-was-coming.html |date=20120721060916 }}, turkishweekly.net, dated 19 July 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://libertarianreview.us/2012/07/20/netanyahu-blames-iran-for-attack-in-bulgaria-in-record-time/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-10-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825194747/http://libertarianreview.us/2012/07/20/netanyahu-blames-iran-for-attack-in-bulgaria-in-record-time/ |archivedate=2012-08-25 }}</ref>

==背景==
这起爆炸案发生的前一个月，在[[印度|印度]]、[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]、[[泰国|泰国]]、[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]等地发生了多起针对以色列游客或外交官的袭击或未遂袭击。这些袭击被认为是杀害[[伊朗|伊朗]]参与秘密核试验的核科学家的报复行为。伊朗方面与[[真主党|真主党]]暗指了这些袭击事件。<ref name="NYTIndia">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/17/world/asia/indian-police-issue-warrants-for-iranian-citizens-in-bombing.html | title=India’s Blast Inquiry Tests Ties to Israel and Iran | work=The New York Times | date=16 March 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Yardley, Jim | archive-date=2019-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203121520/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/17/world/asia/indian-police-issue-warrants-for-iranian-citizens-in-bombing.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="USAThailand">{{cite news | url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/story/2012-02-16/thailand-plot-israelis/53113804/1 | title=Thailand: Iranians planned to attack Israelis | work=USA Today | date=16 February 2012 | agency=AP | accessdate=18 July 2012 | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205316/http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/story/2012-02-16/thailand-plot-israelis/53113804/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>在布尔加斯的这场爆炸不过几天前，一名为真主党效力的人试图在塞浦路斯发动袭击，但是被捕。<ref name="HaaretzCyprus">{{cite news | url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/man-detained-in-cyprus-was-planning-attack-on-israeli-targets-for-hezbollah-1.451000 | title=Man detained in Cyprus was planning attack on Israeli targets for Hezbollah | work=Ha'aretz | date=14 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Ravid, Barak | archive-date=2015-10-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015233343/http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/man-detained-in-cyprus-was-planning-attack-on-israeli-targets-for-hezbollah-1.451000 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年1月，在一辆从[[土耳其|土耳其]]开往[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]满载以色列人的汽车上发现一件可疑的包裹，之后以色列方面要求它的公民提高安全警惕。<ref name="JPostReport">{{cite news | url=http://www.jpost.com/International/Article.aspx?id=277989 | title=7 dead in bombing of Israeli bus in Burgas | work=The Jerusalem Post | date=18 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Katz, Yaakov, and Keinon, Herb, and Lappin, Yaakov | archive-date=2013-05-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525203933/http://www.jpost.com/International/Article.aspx?id=277989 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==袭击==
爆炸发生在黑海名胜[[布尔加斯|布尔加斯]]的机场附近。这是一个有约200,000居民的城市，距离保加利亚首都[[索菲亚|索菲亚]]东约400[[千米|千米]]。爆炸共造成7人死亡，至少32人受伤。<ref>{{cite news|last=Krasimirov|first=Angel|title=Bulgaria Bus Blast: Suicide Bomber Killed 8 On Vehicle Transporting Israeli Tourists (VIDEO, PHOTOS)|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/19/bulgaria-bus-blast-suicide-bomber_n_1685211.html|accessdate=19 July 2012|newspaper=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|date=19 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723105826/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/19/bulgaria-bus-blast-suicide-bomber_n_1685211.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=TimesIsrael>{{cite news|title=7 dead, 3 critical after attack on Israeli tourists in Bulgaria|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/explosion-rocks-israeli-tour-bus-in-bulgaria/|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=The Times of Israel|date=18 July 2012|author=Michal Shmulovich|author2=Ilan Ben Zion|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208210951/https://www.timesofisrael.com/explosion-rocks-israeli-tour-bus-in-bulgaria/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Reuters>{{cite news|last=Tsolova|first=Tsvetelia|title=Israel blames Iran for Bulgaria bus bomb that kills six|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/18/us-bulgaria-explosion-idUSBRE86H0YX20120718|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=Reuters|date=18 July 2012|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327074805/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/18/us-bulgaria-explosion-idUSBRE86H0YX20120718|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CNN>{{cite news|title=Israelis killed in Bulgaria bus terror attack, minister says|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/07/18/world/europe/bulgaria-israel-blast/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=CNN|date=18 July 2012|author=|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816115646/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/07/18/world/europe/bulgaria-israel-blast/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Haaretz>{{cite news|title=7 reported killed in terror attack against Israelis in Bulgaria|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/at-least-7-killed-in-terror-attack-against-israelis-in-bulgaria-1.452013|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=Haaretz|date=18 July 2012|author=Barak Ravid|author2=Zohar Blumenkrantz|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911193227/https://www.haaretz.com/7-reported-killed-in-attack-against-israelis-in-bulgaria-1.5267839|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=RT>{{cite news|title=Tourist terror: At least seven Israelis killed in Bulgaria bus bomb attack (PHOTOS, VIDEO)|url=http://www.rt.com/news/israeli-tourists-bus-explosion-498/|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=Russia Today|date=18 July 2012|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111230241/https://www.rt.com/news/israeli-tourists-bus-explosion-498/|dead-url=no}}</ref>另有两辆巴士在在爆炸中受损。<ref name="JPostReport">{{cite news | url=http://www.jpost.com/International/Article.aspx?id=277989 | title=7 dead in bombing of Israeli bus in Burgas | work=The Jerusalem Post|date=18 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Katz, Yaakov, and Keinon, Herb, and Lappin, Yaakov}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ajc.com/news/nation-world/bulgaria-says-israelis-killed-1480640.html Bulgaria says Israelis killed by suicide attacker] by Veselin Toshkov [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] 19 July 2012 </ref>

保加利亚领导人，包括总统[[罗森·普列夫内利耶夫|罗森·普列夫内利耶夫]]在内，立即赶赴事发地点。外交部表示，官方确认这是一次恐怖袭击。<ref name="HuffPoAttack">{{cite news | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/18/bulgaria-bus-blast-israeli-tourists_n_1683204.html | title=Bulgaria Bus Blast: 6 Dead, Dozens Wounded As Explosion Hits Bus Carrying Young Israeli Tourists | work=The Huffington Post | date=18 July 2012 | agency=Associated Press | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Toshkov, Veselin, and Heller, Aron | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305052401/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/18/bulgaria-bus-blast-israeli-tourists_n_1683204.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

受伤的乘客包括一名11岁的孩子，两名怀孕的妇女。<ref name="YNetAttack">{{cite web | url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4257492,00.html | title=7 killed in terror attack on Israeli tourists in Bulgaria | publisher=Yedioth Ahronot | date=18 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Somfalvi, Attila | archive-date=2020-11-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120030515/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4257492,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>保加利亚的巴士司机在此次爆炸中身亡。<ref name="fakeUSID" />爆炸的幸存者描述，爆炸时人被冲击力抛入空中，看到尸体的碎片，人们哭喊与尖叫。目击者称，爆炸开始于车辆头部，之后车辆迅速着火。一些乘客从窗户跳出车辆来逃生。<ref name="JPostSurvivor">{{cite web | url=http://www.jpost.com/NationalNews/Article.aspx?id=278028 | title=Bus bomb survivor: 'There were bodies all around' | publisher=The Jerusalem Post | date=18 July 2012 | accessdate=18 July 2012 | author=Lappin, Yaakov | archive-date=2013-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316233857/http://www.jpost.com/NationalNews/Article.aspx?id=278028 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

袭击发生两天后，保加利亚内政部长{{link-en|Tsvetan Tsvetanov|Tsvetan Tsvetanov}}表示，炸弹是在一个男子背包中的，这位男子在机场的摄像头中出现过。他还说，炸弹在大巴的行李箱中被引爆，相当于3千克的[[TNT|TNT]]。<ref name="BombTNT">{{cite web | url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/bulgaria-still-struggling-to-confirm-attackers-identity/ | title=Burgas bomb was TNT device hidden in backpack, Bulgarian minister says | publisher=The Times of Israel | date=July 20, 2012 | accessdate=July 20, 2012 | author=Yaakov, Yifa, and Ben Zion, Ilan | archive-date=2019-12-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205004413/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bulgaria-still-struggling-to-confirm-attackers-identity/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

